data.description: This contemporary Farmhouse is situated in the sought-after Farmville area, just a brief 10-minute drive from Vidant. Offering three bedrooms, two spacious bathrooms, and a fully finished bonus room, this home boasts an array of appealing features. Enjoy the charm of covered front and rear porches, equipped with gutters featuring a rain-chain and collection barrel for exterior watering. For outdoor cooking enthusiasts, there's a grilling patio complete with a natural gas hookup.The exterior of the house is a harmonious blend of vinyl, stone, and a metal roof accent on the front, giving it a modern yet rustic appeal. Inside, you'll find an open and inviting layout with a front-facing kitchen featuring quartz countertops, a convenient walk-in pantry, a gas range with a pot filler, a stainless steel farmhouse sink, open shelving, and cabinetry with soft-close features. The spacious center island is perfect for food preparation, and makes a great hang out for the family,  and there's even a wine fridge for your favorite vintages. The fixtures throughout the home exhibit a striking combination of black and champagne finishes.The living area is a highlight, with its vaulted ceiling, decorative ceiling beams, and an impressive 5-foot fireplace. The adjacent dining room exudes elegance with wainscoting and accent lighting, creating a warm and welcoming space for gatherings.The master bedroom is a luxurious retreat, featuring wainscoting, recessed lighting, and a private tiled bath that includes a shower with a rain head and hand sprayer,  and a barn-door entry. Bedrooms 2 and 3 share a hall bath with a separate shower and commode room, along with a double vanity for added convenience.This home also offers a double car garage with an exit door and pegboard for organization, a gas tankless water heater for energy efficiency, and foil-backed sheathing in the attic to help maintain a comfortable climate year-round.
